data.description: Check out this wonderful house located in the Bella Verano community. Built in 2019 with a beautiful open floor plan that accentuates the kitchen, with upgraded silent close cabinets, granite countertops, and a gas range. The floor plan allows for easy entertaining by the designed flow of space from kitchen to living area, with access to a beautiful outside patio that has been upgraded with a paver area that is perfect for grilling and an artificial turfed area for practicing putting, or as a play area. The master bedroom is spacious, with an on-suite bathroom and large walk-in closet that will surely delight any clothes enthusiast. The windows are large and provide plenty of natural light which adds to the already inviting feel. The higher ceiling combined with taller framed doors provides a sense of openness and elegance to the interior throughout. The house is outfitted with a wired speaker system to enable direct hookups for listening to music. The bedrooms each have ample closet space and there is a bonus room which could be used as another entertainment space, or as extra bedding space if needed. This community has quick access to both I-4 and 192, and is a short drive to Disney World and the other entertainment venues in Orlando. Welcome home, with a low HOA and no CDD, this house is waiting for you. Has great potential as a residence, or an investment property.
